{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"daf01e4553","title":"对胡军勿作优敌，应尽力争取","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"aca31f0306","index":0,"year":1936,"month":11,"day":30,"articleId":"daf01e4553"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"146ddefcd8","type":"paragraph","text":"对胡军勿作优敌，应尽力争取！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"daf01e4553"},{"id":"7a6fceb190","type":"paragraph","text":"1936年11月30日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"daf01e4553"},{"id":"45e37c262a","type":"paragraph","text":"我们完全同意张的建议，希望立即采取如下具体办法：（一）首先释放一部分仔房，勿骂其长官。（二）用诚息和气与尊重彼方态度，分别写信致胡宗南、孔令、周祥初。（三）派人到豫旺见胡。（四）用毛、朱、张、周及各方面军各军团各军首长名义，发表告胡军官佐士兵书，简单明了说明停战议和、一致抗日的志愿。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"daf01e4553"},{"id":"aec72930a1","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东致彭德怀电的主要内容。该电报通报胡宗南败后其内部充满联俄容共、一致抗日空气，张学良建议“对胡军勿作优敌，应尽力争取”。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"daf01e4553"}],"page":{"id":"cdceff8197","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"daf01e4553","start":25,"end":25}}}},"__N_SSG":true}